defmodule Solution do
  @spec find_prime_pairs(n :: integer) :: [[integer]]
  def find_prime_pairs(n) do
    1..n
    |> Enum.filter(&prime?(&1))
    |> Enum.filter(fn x -> x <= n - x and prime?(n - x) end)
    |> Enum.map(&[&1, n - &1])
  end

  defp prime?(1), do: false
  defp prime?(2), do: true
  defp prime?(n) do
    Enum.none?(2..div(n, 2), &rem(n, &1) == 0)
  end
end
